1
00:00:01,540 --> 00:00:05,380
I heard Yuki got suspended for fighting.

2
00:00:06,210 --> 00:00:08,130
It's all my fault...

3
00:00:08,130 --> 00:00:11,720
It's not your fault.
Those guys are the ones to blame.

4
00:00:14,060 --> 00:00:19,850
Speaking of which, the school festival is right around the corner.
What on earth is Yuki thinking?

5
00:00:21,400 --> 00:00:24,610
Will I be able to do my own makeup...?

6
00:00:25,030 --> 00:00:27,990
I'll help you!

7
00:00:28,990 --> 00:00:31,660
Alright! It's settled then.

8
00:00:31,660 --> 00:00:33,610
Let's go over to Yuki's and have some drinks!

9
00:00:34,380 --> 00:00:35,830
And have a strategy meeting while we're at it!

10
00:00:35,830 --> 00:00:36,700
Yeah!

11
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:38,330
Let's go! C'mon!

12
00:00:50,220 --> 00:00:53,180
Is he not home?

13
00:00:53,180 --> 00:00:55,350
He hasn't even read my texts.

14
00:00:56,260 --> 00:00:59,180
You don't think... he passed out in there, do you?

15
00:00:59,180 --> 00:01:02,560
No way! That's awful!
I'll go get the landlord!

16
00:01:02,560 --> 00:01:04,150
- Whoa! I'm so sorry!
- Ah!

17
00:01:04,150 --> 00:01:05,360
Are you okay?

18
00:01:05,360 --> 00:01:08,030
It was my fault, I wasn't looking where I was going.

19
00:01:08,030 --> 00:01:09,440
Here, you dropped this.

20
00:01:09,440 --> 00:01:10,860
Oh...

21
00:01:11,400 --> 00:01:16,030
Huh? You wouldn't happen to be... Makoto-kun?

22
00:01:17,910 --> 00:01:19,750
Yes...
